    <content type="html">&lt;section id="pewpew-standalone"&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A Python-based micro game console, optimized for game development workshops.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="project-thumb"&gt;
&lt;a class="reference external image-reference" href="/_images/5267771533379701591.jpg"&gt;&lt;img alt="projects/project-159733/images/5267771533379701591.jpg" src="projects/project-159733/images/5267771533379701591.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
