    <updated>2019-04-11T00:00:00+02:00</updated>
    <content type="html">&lt;section id="pybadge-hacking"&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hacking on Adafruit’s PyBadge&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="project-thumb"&gt;
&lt;a class="reference external image-reference" href="/_images/4208061554992232926.jpg"&gt;&lt;img alt="projects/project-164929/images/4208061554992232926.jpg" src="projects/project-164929/images/4208061554992232926.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a class="reference external image-reference" href="/_images/5699241554979302535.jpg"&gt;&lt;img alt="projects/project-164929/images/5699241554979302535.jpg" src="projects/project-164929/images/5699241554979302535.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a class="reference external image-reference" href="/_images/2592411555151890169.jpg"&gt;&lt;img alt="projects/project-164929/images/2592411555151890169.jpg" src="projects/project-164929/images/2592411555151890169.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight-none notranslate"&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;Adafruit&amp;#39;s PyBadge is coming soon, and I got my hands on a prototype.
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Now I will do science to it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What is PyBadge? It’s a handheld device the size of a credit card with
a display, a bunch of buttons, a microcontroller running CircuitPython
and a bunch of extras (neopixels, accelerometer, speaker, flash
storage, battery charging, light sensor). It is also a secretly a
Feather, as you can connect FeatherWings to it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It is similar to, but much more powerful than my earlier project &lt;a class="reference internal" href="../../../projects/project-27629/#project-27629"&gt;&lt;span class="std std-ref"&gt;µGame&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (and the reason why I paused work on &lt;span class="xref std std-ref"&gt;project-86818&lt;/span&gt; ). I should be able to get my libraries and games from µGame to run on
it, but I hope that I can also do some other fun things with it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;iframe style="width: 500px; height: 281px;" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="None" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/HT4XKfFpWoo"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
